king khalid international airport ( arabic : مطار الملك خالد الدولي ; maṭār al - malik khālid al - duwaliyy , ) is located   north of riyadh , saudi arabia , designed by the architectural firm hok , and arabian bechtel company limited served as the construction manager on behalf of the saudi government .

asian capitals : this capital is served by king khalid international airport , which lies about 20 miles north of the city

